    public class RefinedPeak<P extends Localizable>
extends RealPoint
    A RealPoint representing a sub-pixel-localized peak. Contains the original non-refined peak, a value, and a boolean validity flag. See SubpixelLocalization.
    Author:
    Tobias Pietzsch
